description: Summa Silver Corp., a silver and gold development company, engages in acquiring, exploring, and evaluating natural resource properties in the United States. The company holds a 100% interest in the Hughes property that covers an area of 5,504 acres located in central Nevada. It also has an option to earn a 100% interest in the Mogollon Property located in New Mexico. The company was formerly known as Pinnacle North Gold Corp. and changed its name to Summa Silver Corp. in April 2020. Summa Silver Corp. was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Galen Stuart McNamara B.Sc., M.Sc., P.Geo
